Moody's Investors Service Inc said itdowngraded to Baa-2 from A-3 the rating on Loral Corp's 7-1/4pct convertible subordinated debentures of 2010 and on 10-3/4pct subordinated sinking fund debentures due 1997.    Moody's said it took the action, which affectsapproximately 117 mln dlrs of debt, after examining Loral'sacquisition of Goodyear Aerospace Corp.    It said the downgrade reflects the substantial increase inthe company's debt in order to finance the acquisition and therisks of assimilating such a relatively large acquisition. Reuter&#3;